\end{equation}

\end_inset

It is convenient to reformulate these conditions in terms of 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

as 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
b<1 & \text{and } & a<2b+3b^{2}\,,
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
1\leq b<\frac{3+\sqrt{15}}{3} & \text{and } & a<2+6b+3b^{2}\,.
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

In particular, we obtain that for 
\begin_inset Formula $b>1+\sqrt{5/3}$
\end_inset

